('5 Best Printers for Students in India', 'Choosing the perfect printer for your needs may not be easy as it would appear. There are several types of printers available. Choosing the right kind of option for the students may not be easy. If you are looking for a printer for your needs in an enhanced printing experience for the students, this compilation of the best printers for students in India should be helpful for you. We have made it a point to include every printer type in this compilation so that you can choose the right technology that meets your exact needs. \r\n\r\nWhy do Students Need a Printer?\r\nStudents need to get print outs for a host of printing jobs as part of their projects, assignments, and a host of other tasks. Having to depend upon a cyber caf? or a print shop may not be economical when you have to print frequently. It can be quite convenient and cost saving when it comes to buying a printer for your home or business. \r\n\r\nThere are situations where you would need a print out at odd hours. Maybe you need a print of air ticket or a report you completed into the late night. However, buying a printer may not be as easy as it would appear to.  Let us check out the best printers that can get the work done for the students. \r\n\r\nWhat factors should you check for in a Printer ? A Perfect Buying Guide \r\nAs with any product, you would need to focus on a few key parameters before you can actually buy a new printer. Let?s focus on the best features you should focus on. \r\n\r\n\r\nTypes of Printers\r\nThe printers basically come in three variants ? Ink tank printers, Inkjet printers, and Laser printers. Of course, there are other types of printers that are normally used for specific purposes like Dot matrix that are used only for accounting and similar other requirements. \r\n\r\nHere are the little details about the best features offered by each of these printer types. \r\n\r\nTop 5 Best Printers for Students\r\nHaving gone through the complete information on how to choose your printer, here are a few excellent choices for the best printers a student can make use of. We will check out the printers across multiple technologies and types to arrive at the best options that would help you achieve the best standards. \r\n\r\nThe printers listed here are shortlisted after studying the well-known best printers for college students reviews. \r\n\r\n\r\nHP DeskJet 3636 All-in-One Ink Advantage Printer\r\nStudents need a low-cost printing advantage, and the HP DeskJet 3636 All-in-One Ink Advantage Printer should be a great choice. You also have access to mobile printing and wireless connectivity options. If you are looking for the best borderless printing experience, the HP printer should provide you with an extreme experience and worthy of being the first option in the list of best printers for students in India.\r\n\r\nEpson L565 Wi-Fi All-in-One Ink Tank Printer\r\nThis is an ink tank printer and may be quite expensive enough. However, if you are into high-end options for printing, this can be a good option for your needs as a student. It can print, scan and copy along with the functioning as an option for receiving a fax. It can be one of the best options among the best printer for college students. \r\n\r\nSamsung SCX-3401 Multi-Function Monochrome Laser Printer\r\nIf you do not need any sort of colour prints and are happy with the black and white prints for your needs, this may be a perfect choice for almost all your printing needs. The multi-function capability of the printer makes it a perfect option for students. \r\nWhich Printer should a Student opt for?\r\nWell, there is nothing specific in printers aimed for the students. However, if you are looking for an average functionality, a monochrome printer that can provide faster printing performance should be an excellent option. Pages and pages of the coursework, assignment, and projects being printed faster enough should be a great option for most of your needs. \r\n\r\nHowever, if you are into the creative field like graphics and similar other genres, you would need a multifunction inkjet printer. Of course, the ability to print online or through smartphones can definitely be an added advantage. \r\n\r\nWhile Inkjet printers are available at a lower price bracket, the laser printers turn out to be more economical with their affordable toners and consumables. \r\n\r\nConclusion\r\nBefore we conclude, it may be worthwhile to mention that we have prepared this list based on the analysis we conducted for the best printers for students that including the best printer for college students. That should explain the reason for including a couple of high-end options in this compilation of the best printers for students in India. \r\n\r\nIn any case, the best printers outlined in this comparison and the buying guide associated herewith should provide you with an efficient platform for choosing the best printers for students in India. Pick up the best that meets your preferences and share your experiences with us.\r\n', 2, '2019-10-02 08:46:36', 5, 'img/printer.png', 34, 1),
('How to Use an Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC?', '\r\nThe Android devices have become quite popular and much-used ones in recent times. They have made it possible to work with practically any need you may have. The on the go performance would make it one of the best options in every right. But, have you ever given a thought to how these can be a good option to work with your other devices as a remote control?\r\nWell, not sure about the remote, but you can definitely use your Android device as a keyboard and a trackpad. For the sake of this post, we will check out the ways that you can use your Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC. We will also cover a little detail on use android phone as a mouse via USB.\r\n\r\nHow to use Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC?\r\nIf you are looking to use your Android phone as USB keyboard for PC, you would need to have access to a few specialised apps. So, let us check out a few good options on how to use Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC. Below are those apps that you need to use Android phone as USB keyboard for your computer.:\r\n\r\nMonect Mobile\r\nThis is one of the most popular a capable options for controlling your PC with your Android device. It can be a good option to control your Windows PC with ease and simplicity. The Monect PC Remote is available on a variety of devices and platforms like Android and iOS.\r\n\r\nThe app lets you control your device into a keyboard and trackpad device as also joystick, media controller and a host of other options. You can connect the two devices with ease and simplicity. As long as you have both your computer and Android device connected to the same WiFi network, you can work easily with it.\r\n\r\nThe app is best suited for converting your Android device into a remote control by every right, and that includes the functionality to use your Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC. The different modes can help you arrive at the best possible options to use Android phone as mouse via USB or use it for a wide range of different options and needs.\r\n\r\nIntel Remote Keyboard\r\nThis is yet another excellent option developed by Intel Corporation and offers you a perfect option for your needs in how to Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC. The keyboard is available on Windows 8.1 and Windows 10 users. The device pairs with your Windows device through a wireless connection and lets you use it as the Windows keyboard.\r\n\r\nIn fact, you can even use it at any distance as long as your WiFi connectivity supports it. The app can even be the best bet to use Android phone as mouse via USB. Do note that you will need to download the host app on your Windows device so that you can use it with your Android app with ease. The application is free to use, and you would find no issues in downloading and use it.\r\n\r\ngPad\r\nThe gPad is one of the perfect options for use with the keyboard functionality on your Android device. Make sure you have the gPad client on your Android device and install the gPad Server Client on your computer. The app works with both Mac and Windows devices.\r\n\r\nThe connectivity can be established with the help of USB, WiFi connection and even via Bluetooth. The app works in an excellent manner to offer you several possibilities. This can work in an excellent manner for use with your gaming or movie viewing requirements. No matter whether you would want to use Android phone as mouse via USB or the Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC.\r\n\r\nRemote Mouse\r\nThis is one of the perfect options to use as a trackpad, keyboard or even mouse with your Windows device. The app is specifically designed to work as a perfect option to use Android phone as mouse via USB; it can also double up as an equally great option as Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC.\r\n\r\nThe application works in an excellent manner to bring the remote control features to your Android device. The fully simulated experience offered by the app should be what makes it a great performer. The high-end rating offered by the remote App would be what should make it one of the perfect options to work with your Windows device. The service remains almost similar to the other apps listed here. You should install the app on your Android device and an equivalent mouse server on your Windows system.\r\n\r\nThere are several apps and tools available that can help you achieve the best results when it comes to the usability of your mobile device as your mouse. In fact, each of the apps would be helpful enough in arriving at the excellent options to use Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC or use android phone as mouse via USB.\r\n\r\nYou can make sure that you are connected to both the devices on the same WiFi network. In essence, this should be one of the perfect options to use if you really want to use it for enhancing your productivity levels. Yet another excellent option that it can provide you is in case of the presentations that you run. Running the presentations with ease with the help of the keyboard or mouse app should be one of the best options to go with.\r\n\r\nWorking remotely with your tasks is one of the most prevalent options these days. If you do not want to carry the laptop around and work with ease with your emote keyboard and mouse functioning, the apps we have listed here should be the right options you can check out.\r\n\r\nThose were a few great options that should help you achieve the best options if you are looking to use Android Phone as USB keyboard for PC. Not that the list is exhaustive in any manner as such. We have just ensured that the apps in this list offer you an easy to use the option to use Android phone as mouse via USB as well in addition to using it as the keyboard.', 1, '2019-10-02 08:52:29', 6, 'img/How-to-Use-an-Android-Phone-as-USB-keyboard-for-PC.png', 35, 7),
('Utopia ? Keep your Communication Private {Review}', 'The privacy protection these days has been a huge issue. In fact, the world is moving towards complete surveillance. Lack of privacy has been a difficult issue to handle. How about a service that would be helpful in protecting your privacy? This is where a platform named Utopia should come in handy enough.\r\n\r\nUtopia ? An Excellent Option to Keep your Communication Private\r\nWell, Utopia is a feature-rich platform that should be helpful enough in protecting the privacy of your communication. If you are someone who is fond of privacy and treat it one of the most essential elements in any sort of communication.\r\n\r\nIt works on the basis of the decentralised ecosystem and lets you communicate through text or voice messages. You can also use it to transfer the files and even send internal emails. It is an application created for Windows and Mac OS X. The platform was created by a team of networking enthusiasts and designed as a means of offering a complete freedom, privacy and lack of censorship of any nature.\r\n\r\nUtopia has been under development since 2013 and has been released as a beta since July, 4th. The platform fully decentralized, based on a peer to peer network and lets you communicate with practically anyone whenever and wherever you want to. This will provide you access to guaranteed freedom of speech.\r\n\r\nHow Does it Work?\r\nYou just need to log in to the platform and start sending and receiving the messages or voice recordings with ease. The platform uses high-end cryptography for the purpose of securing your communication.\r\n\r\nUtopia also offers you access to uMail, which is an excellent alternative to the email communication. What makes it even impressive is the fact that it can be easy and simple to work with. It comes with a familiar look as any of your favourite email services ? you have an inbox, trash folder, and even the filters to avoid getting emails from specific services.\r\n\r\nThere is no limit to the size and number files you would be able to share with your contacts. There is practically any file that you would need to send to your friends and colleagues.\r\n\r\nWhat are the specific features that would make it an excellent option?\r\nYou can join Utopia as a Tester, Contributor, or a Promoter. In fact, each of these categories has rewards for completing actions strived to improve Utopia. Do note that the program is under beta and a few features currently available may be discontinued or new features may be added in due course.\r\n\r\nThe encryption functionality offered by the platform would definitely make it a formidable choice. While every member can take part in the communication of data, it will only be decrypted by the actual recipient. The high degree of encryption ensures that the communication is free from any sort of interception. The complete communication is entirely secure. The data is encrypted using Curve25519 high-speed elliptic curve cryptography. You have access to 256-bit AES encryption.\r\n\r\nYet another excellent option available on the service would include built-in uWallet feature available on the platform. You can use it to send or receive payments through internao cryptocurrency names Crypton. You can pay using Crypto cards as well without the need for revealing your identity and even Utopia public key. You can accept payments for your services using the Crypton currency as a merchant. A purely simplified option for a financial security should be what it would provide you access to.\r\n\r\nYou also have access to an alternative to the traditional domain name service in the form of Utopia Name System or uNS. Once you register a name through uNS, it is yours forever. This is the decentralised registry of names and can be used without a fear of issues.\r\n\r\nWant to Join Utopia? Here is how..\r\nWell, Utopia has gone into public beta. If you want to be a tester, contributor or a promoter, just join the Utopia Beta Program and you are good to go. The official release is scheduled for October, 2019.\r\n\r\nThe participation can take place in several formats. You can take up testing, multiple forms of promotion or even you can provide support for other users or moderate Utopia channel in your region. You can take up a single role or try yourself in multiple roles. Each of these rewards would be accompanied by specific rewards.\r\n\r\nUtopia is a P2P Project management. You can both participate in a new technology and opt for a huge financial gain. Each of the actions you undertake will get you rewarded. You will be able to earn rewards based on the roles you are looking to take part in.\r\n\r\nIf you get involved for beta testing, you will earn for your efforts in testing the network. You will be paid for every effort you want to put in improving the Utopia platform. If you are a contributor, you will be able to drive users to the Utopia platform. This can be done in several ways that include providing content through blogs, forums and a few other resources. The rewards you get would be dependent upon the efforts you put in.\r\n\r\nYou can also earn rewards as a promoter, and this would have no limit as long as you attempt to be as much creative as possible.\r\n\r\nIn Conclusion\r\nUtopia is indeed an excellent platform and wants to revolutionize industry of peer-to-peer software and entire data security sector. In fact, it has placed a huge onus on the users of the platform, and it would be the users like you and us that will be determining the direction of the platform. As a user of the platform in any role, you can place suggestions about the new features you would want to see within the platform.\r\n\r\nThe platform is designed to bring in a huge improvement in the days to come. A platform that promises a high end privacy and data security can be one of the best options.\r\n\r\nIn fact, in a situation where our identity and privacy are sold without any fault on your part, such a platform can indeed be a huge value addition. We would definitely look ahead for a further development of the platform in the days to come. Make a change to the way the world sends messages and join the platform today!\r\n', 2, '2019-10-02 08:59:42', 7, 'img/utopia-708x320.png', 36, 6),
('5 Questions to Ask Yourself Before Choosing Point of Sale Software', '\r\nPOS software is more advanced than ever, with many POS systems providing extras such as employee tracking, analytics tools, and real-time sales number and activity overviews. With such amazing features, it?s easy to see why many businesses are upgrading their outdated POS systems for these modern alternatives. Here are some questions you should ask yourself before choosing new point of sale software for your business.\r\n\r\nDoes The Software Come With Dedicated Customer Support?\r\nThis is crucial to choosing the right POS software for your business. Without a good customer support system, your new software may wind up being a hindrance rather than an advantage. Any software should have a dedicated support staff behind it because you can be sure that any technology will malfunction at some point.\r\n\r\nA dedicated support staff will assist you in navigating any complex issues that arise with your POS system, as well as help to answer questions about the limitations and extra features of the software itself.\r\n\r\nHaving answers to difficult questions will ensure that your POS system functions properly at all times, helping you avoid frustrated customers and employees. There?s nothing worse than a malfunction during checkout that you don?t have the answer to. Problems such as this can cause your customers to lose faith in the competence of your staff, as well as patience with the checkout process itself.\r\n\r\nWhere Do I Complete Most of My Business Transactions?\r\nThe answer to this question will help you choose a POS system that is more suited to the needs of your business. If you?re doing a large portion of business online, you may want to choose a POS system like Shopify, which is specifically designed for e-commerce applications. If you?re a brick and mortar store, Square or Vend may be the better choice.\r\n\r\nWhile Square and Vend also offer e-commerce solutions, it?s best to choose software that is tailored to the exact nature of your business for maximum compatibility. With so many point of sale software options available, choosing the best one for your business can mean the difference between a smooth transition and a difficult one.\r\n\r\nAre My Customers Frustrated With The Checkout Process?\r\nPerhaps the best indicator that it?s time for a new POS system is the frustration of your customers. If you?re noticing customers becoming agitated with a slow or otherwise inefficient checkout process, or receiving written feedback in the form of reviews or complaints, it?s probably a good time to make the switch.\r\n\r\nPay close attention to customer feedback and identify what exactly about the process is frustrating for them. Is it the speed of the checkout process? Or perhaps the overall process itself is simply inefficient? These questions can best be answered by those that use the system the most.\r\n\r\nToo much frustration with your checkout process will likely cause even loyal customers to seek out another brand. Never underestimate the power of an efficient checkout process. Moving customers through the line quickly can leaving them feeling stress-free and more likely to purchase from your business in the future.\r\n\r\nWhat Security Features Does The Software Offer?\r\nAny time you?re dealing with money, security should be your number one concern; especially if you?re dealing with someone else?s money. Your customers will want to be sure that they?re swiping credit and debit cards in a secure system, as breaches can cause monetary damages and leave you accountable for the intrusion.\r\n\r\nLook into your next POS system?s security features before making a choice for your business. Be sure that both hardware and software are secure when running debit or credit cards, and that the company behind your POS software provides support staff and security breach protocols.\r\n\r\nWhat Does It Cost?\r\nAt last, we come to the one question that every business will ask: what does it cost? This is an important factor in choosing your next POS system, as there are many freeware POS systems available. Just remember that the general rule ?you get what you pay for? applies here as well.\r\n\r\nChoosing a POS system by price depends on a number of factors. What does it cost monthly (or annually)? Can my business afford the cost of the POS system and its hardware? Do I need to purchase my own tablet or other hardware?\r\n\r\nIdentifying all cost factors of your new POS system will help you decide on a package that best suits the needs of your business. Many modern POS software providers offer basic packages for small businesses or e-commerce sites, a premium or middle package for larger franchises, and an enterprise option for large chains.\r\n\r\nThe industry your business operates in can also have an effect on the cost of your POS system. For instance, a grocery POS system generally costs more than a bar POS system. Choosing between high and low-end software also affects price, with high-end POS software costing about 1.5-2 times as much as its low-end counterparts.\r\n\r\nConclusion\r\n\r\nChoosing a POS solution for your business is easier than ever with the limitless information available on the web. There are hundreds of POS options to choose from, so with a little research, you?re sure to find the one that works for you. Always check the security features, support options, and cost of the software beforehand. Informed decisions always cost less in the end.\r\n', 1, '2019-10-02 09:01:23', 7, 'img/pos.jpg', 37, 23);

